  Description: You are a descendant of a famed crafter and have your own amazing
    talent. Other dwarves might consider this a blessing from your ancestors or from
    the Forgefather himself, depending on where you grew up. You become trained in
    Crafting (or another skill if you were already trained in Crafting) and gain
    the Specialty Crafting skill feat, but you can pick two different specialties
    instead of one.
